{"tid":460622,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國留學]如果雪櫃壞左點樣暫時處理入面啲生肉","createTime":"2017-11-06T22:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T23:14:04.000Z","uid":92569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9bd856f03902cf2f687e3b05a3a93eb6e068a1be","tid":460622,"uid":92569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:49:40.000Z","msg":"琴日下晏買完餸一返到屋企就發現個雪櫃壞左<br />\n其實我係咁啱留意到個雪櫃無左平時製冷既聲音先知道<br />\n一路見佢有燈著以為冇事<br />\n點知入面啲野完全唔凍<br />\n我自己又唔想麻煩到鄰居, 又唔知佢地幾時得閒比我入屋<br />\n所以都係自己搞掂算<br />\nCall左agent, 話星期四先有人黎搞<br />\n問題黎啦, 咁我買返黎啲餸點搞呢?<br />\n我諗過<br />\n首先將啲肉煮熟哂佢, 我諗咁樣無咁易發臭同生菌?<br />\n之後再將啲肉放入個碗, 再用保鮮紙包實<br />\n最後放入一個大既保鮮盒再加滿水<br />\n由於我身處既地方都幾凍下, 重要啱啱轉左冬令<br />\n所以就將計就計, 放個設置好既保鮮盒放到窗口位<br />\n唔知咁樣會唔會掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bde71ba5baab4782df41a7e0b3d1b066cf1cea","tid":460622,"uid":15243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琴日下晏買完餸一返到屋企就發現個雪櫃壞左<br />\n其實我係咁啱留意到個雪櫃無左平時製冷既聲音先知道<br />\n一路見佢有燈著以為冇事<br />\n點知入面啲野完全唔凍<br />\n我自己又唔想麻煩到鄰居, 又唔知佢地幾時得閒比我入屋<br />\n所以都係自己搞掂算<br />\nCall左agent, 話星期四先有人黎搞<br />\n問題黎啦, 咁我買返黎啲餸點搞呢?<br />\n我諗過<br />\n首先將啲肉煮熟哂佢, 我諗咁樣無咁易發臭同生菌?<br />\n之後再將啲肉放入個碗, 再用保鮮紙包實<br />\n最後放入一個大既保鮮盒再加滿水<br />\n由於我身處既地方都幾凍下, 重要啱啱轉左冬令<br />\n所以就將計就計, 放個設置好既保鮮盒放到窗口位<br />\n唔知咁樣會唔會掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n包實放係balcony 起碼頂到一日 如果天氣夠凍 雪埋汽水都仲得"},{"pid":"f5b8a638ad504412946a03f37344090629d41395","tid":460622,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:54:56.000Z","msg":"有鹽醃曬佢"},{"pid":"d04e7fef2f197c57929fd1de1b1ce114b0fd15fb","tid":460622,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">用</span>鹽醃曬佢</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7c9e147a68741cae9484187c73a9a539cbdaeabd","tid":460622,"uid":47273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:55:22.000Z","msg":"本身雪櫃多少都有保溫功能，多少都隔絕到外界影響，買包冰返黎放入雪櫃，放返野食入去，無咩事就盡量唔好開雪櫃就得<br />\n<br />\n利申 無留過學，非獨居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b769cc4923c4037f6bd40978a3621b50beecdade","tid":460622,"uid":28938,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:55:23.000Z","msg":"自首啦，人肉最尾點都會轉出臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7393c45bc8e91958a2ab3cdf0ddc999a03188693","tid":460622,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:55:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e90e31be3bcc7b220f68068b56e82046ade8c9d","tid":460622,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:56:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49619335062b5484fa82ace9fa1d14c1f9430332","tid":460622,"uid":92569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有幾多生肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n一盒生豬肉碎<br />\n其實呢家聞落已經半盒雞唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲味勁酸"},{"pid":"e374926d9b916a65d5d21db4019b0a73090f9af5","tid":460622,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d8402d8a3d321c62cb4257f72f24f85f970803","tid":460622,"uid":92569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T22:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自首啦，人肉最尾點都會轉出臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我樓下就係警局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最危險既地方係最安全"},{"pid":"580348a93209a39dfffce819a9d4226cede43667","tid":460622,"uid":92569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身雪櫃多少都有保溫功能，多少都隔絕到外界影響，買包冰返黎放入雪櫃，放返野食入去，無咩事就盡量唔好開雪櫃就得<br />\n<br />\n利申 無留過學，非獨居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我呢邊就黎12點夜晚<br />\n應該冇地方可以買包冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224656325801c324d4e4977fa6d4f0eed00c0a28","tid":460622,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自首啦，人肉最尾點都會轉出臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我樓下就係警局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最危險既地方係最安全</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請埋班警察上黎BBQ，醫到肚，毀屍滅跡之餘仲可以令班警察變埋共犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad4d72fbd969ff91965c324dbf2153a1efd1f80","tid":460622,"uid":155256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:05:41.000Z","msg":"UK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800b22351b49a2401dc2c8563ceb4446a191e72d","tid":460622,"uid":92569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>UK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nching係估定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8b200d56090d095443262cc9a4f0a0729457c7","tid":460622,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/071233_fe78c33d413943cd61831962d6cecf0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F071233_fe78c33d413943cd61831962d6cecf0a.jpg&h=b05cb4f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea1f5bfc3b9502c345d583969822ccd7b01d8d0f","tid":460622,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:13:37.000Z","msg":"附近有冇露宿者？煮左分俾佢地食囉"},{"pid":"73058c1ed7baf16e4a835639d69a2d8708fa281e","tid":460622,"uid":92569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T23:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自首啦，人肉最尾點都會轉出臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我樓下就係警局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最危險既地方係最安全</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請埋班警察上黎BBQ，醫到肚，毀屍滅跡之餘仲可以令班警察變埋共犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後埃到新雪櫃黎<br />\n舊雪櫃一拎走就可以攻成身退<br />\n成為一級犯罪家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}